result.reason: Limitation of MSTSCLib RDP ActiveX control — RedirectPrinters is a simple boolean; mstsc.exe uses a richer internal printer enumeration pipeline that is not exposed through the COM API, so mRemoteNG cannot control which or how many printers are forwarded.
result.approach: No feasible fix — the AdvancedSettings2.RedirectPrinters boolean is the only printer-redirection knob exposed by the ActiveX control. Matching mstsc.exe behavior would require bypassing the COM control entirely or using undocumented RDP channel APIs.
